skdetail:

Invocation Name: snowdog word game
des: This is a fun game (think Scategories). Alexa will choose a letter and you and your team have to guess words that have to do with Siberian huskies or other snow dogs. This is a team game. At least two players are needed. Developed by a professional snow dog portrait painter and computer nerd. Have fun!
